    • Constructor Detail

      • OneMap

        public OneMap(String mapName)
        Creates a new OneMap for associating one value with one key. The returned map is not indexed. The returned map is persistent iff the database is.
        Parameters:
        mapName - name for the map. Must be a database-wide unique value.
